Executive Summary & Troubles that occurs on the project 3


Troubles that occurred on the project:


1) The challenge started at the data source. The excel had 155 columns of data and it was a big decision on which of these columns I need to import into Power BI

2) I had challenges on knowing which KPIs to choose from because the industry is wide, and data is very large. I run into several blockage trying to get the best fit that can tell my story.

 3) There were lot of back and forth between the query editor and the report model. I sometimes need to import more columns as I realized I needed information from the source to calculate additional columns.
